	 *
	 *  <pre>
	 *  &lt;s:SkinnablePopUpContainer
	 *    <strong>Events</strong>
	 *    close="<i>No default</i>"
	 *    open="<i>No default</i>"
	 *  /&gt;
	 *  </pre>
